      <title>高盛交易部门认为，在股市下跌之际，买入机会短暂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/goldman-s-trading-desk-sees-brief-window-to-buy-dip-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团的斯科特·鲁布纳 (Scott Rubner) 表示，由于系统性基金的抛售压力减轻，同时企业加大股票回购力度，投资者将在本月底获得短暂的买入机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/goldman-s-trading-desk-sees-brief-window-to-buy-dip-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典倾向于采用捷克式融资方式建设新核反应堆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sweden-leans-toward-czech-style-funding-for-new-nuclear-reactors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典正在考虑与捷克共和国新核反应堆类似的融资方案，以帮助支付未来几十年新核反应堆的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sweden-leans-toward-czech-style-funding-for-new-nuclear-reactors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zillow 称，建筑热潮缓解了住房供应，美国租房者因此获得福利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-renters-get-perks-as-building-boom-eases-supply-zillow-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 Zillow 的一篇新博客文章，美国租房者在签订新合同时获得了优惠，这表明公寓建设的激增正在缓解供应紧张的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-renters-get-perks-as-building-boom-eases-supply-zillow-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 13:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉姆称美联储并未落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-12/the-fed-isn-t-behind-the-curve-rhame-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[FS Investments 首席美国经济学家 Lara Rhame 表示，美联储并不“落后”，也不急于降息。她正在接受“彭博监视”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-12/the-fed-isn-t-behind-the-curve-rhame-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 13:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>B. 赖利因风险披露和与卡恩的关系面临更广泛的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/b-riley-faces-wider-us-probe-on-risk-disclosures-ties-to-kahn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新一轮减记和美国对 B. Riley Financial Inc. 是否向投资者准确说明其财务状况的调查不断扩大之际，该公司股价下跌了一半。]]></description>
