    <item>
      <title>市场关注中国套利，铜价继续反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/copper-resumes-decline-as-surplus-mounts-earlier-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价延续从五个月最低收盘价的反弹势头，因伦敦金属交易所仓库撤回铜价的订单表明中国的需求低迷可能已触底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/copper-resumes-decline-as-surplus-mounts-earlier-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗可能采取报复行动，油价上涨，股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着股市小幅走高，油价延续了自 7 月初以来的首次周线涨势，交易员继续关注伊朗对上个月在德黑兰暗杀哈马斯领导人的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀数据公布前股市小幅走高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/asian-stocks-eye-mixed-start-as-volatility-wanes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待有助于确定美联储下一步行动前景的通胀数据，股市在上周市场崩盘后继续反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/asian-stocks-eye-mixed-start-as-volatility-wanes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 22:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
